<HEADLINE> More ARATS, SEF Exchanges Are Expected (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The eight-point proposal set forth by Jiang Zemin, general
secretary of the Communist Party of China (CPC) Central Committee,
has chartered the direction of relations across the straits
and of China's peaceful reunification, Chen said, and the key in
building the stable, healthy and favorable relations across the
straits and the country's peaceful reunification hinges on
adherence to the one-China principle and holding of political
negotiations.
</P>
