Taiwan Straits will be put to an end officially through
negotiations and knotty problems that affect adversely the growth
of cross-straits relations will be resolved step by step, and
truly satisfy Taiwan compatriots' desire for stability, peace and
development, so as to open up new prospects for the development of
the relations across the straits.
</P>
