<HEADLINE> Davenport Sails into European Tennis Final </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, October 17 (Xinhua) - Lindsay Davenport will play for
her sixth title of the year when the World No. 1 defeated
Romanian Irina Spirlea 6-2, 6-3 to reach the final of the
European indoor tennis championship in Zurich on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
The 22-year-old American will take on the winner of the other
semifinal being played later on Saturday between her compatriot
Venus Williams and Frenchwoman Nathalie Tauziat.
</P>
<P>
In both sets Davenport recorded decisive breaks at 2-1 then
held serve, finishing off the 58-minute match with an ace.
</P>
<P>
