<HEADLINE> China's Dalian Export Fair For May 1999 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, October 17 (Xinhua) -- The '99 Dalian Export Fair
will be held in the coastal industrial and tourist city in north
China's Liaoning Province, May 23-28, the organizing committee
announced on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
Machinery, electrical goods, and nonferrous metal products will
be at the top of the list of exhibits, the organizer said, and
foreign companies are being warmly welcomed.
</P>
