The Dalian fair is one of 7 regional trade fairs in China that
are officially approved by the Ministry of Foreign Trade and
Economic Cooperation.
</P>
<P>
Last year, the ministry decided to turn these regional fairs
into specialized trade events, with the one in Dalian focusing on
mechanical, electrical, and nonferrous metal products.  
