<HEADLINE> Bangladeshi PM on Post-Flood Rehabilitation Programs </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, October 17 (Xinhua) -- Bangladeshi Prime Minister Sheikh
Hasina Saturday evening called upon all professionals, social and
cultural activists and leaders and workers, respective of
political parties, to extend cooperation in the post-flood
rehabilitation programs.
</P>
<P>
"Let us all work together to alleviate the sufferings of the
distressed humanity as well as to improve the life-style of the
people," she said in her address to the nation over the radio and
