<HEADLINE> Kuwait Stock Exchange Index Closes Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, October 17 (Xinhua) -- Kuwait Stock Exchange
index closed at 2,064.8 points Saturday, up 23.4 points than that
at Wednesday's closing.
</P>
<P>
However, the turnover slid briefly to 7.31 million Kuwaiti
dinars (24.12 million U.S. dollars) from Wednesday's 8.54 million
dinars (28.18 million dollars).
</P>
<P>
A total of 33.91 million shares changed hands in 1,035 deals
Saturday as against 35.96 million shares in 1,017 deals on last
Wednesday. 
</P>
