<HEADLINE> Brazil Exports More Beef </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
RIO DE JANEIRO, Oct 16 (Xinhua) -- Brazil exported 252,200 tons
of beef during the first eight months this year, a 40.9 percent
increase over the same period of 1997.
</P>
<P>
Statistics from the National Agriculture Confederation show
that Brazil earned 394.6 million U.S. dollars from its beef
exports in the first eight months this year.
</P>
<P>
Brazil is one of the biggest producers and exporters of beef in
the world.
</P>
<P>
