<HEADLINE> Crvena Zvezda to Accept UEFA Decision </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BELGRADE, October 16 (Xinhua) -- Crvena Zvezda Belgrade will
compromised to UEFA's order to play their European tie in Romania
next week because of political tension over Kosovo, a club source
said on Friday.
</P>
