probably make no further appeals to UEFA as scheduled, the source
said.
</P>
<P>
On Thursday, UEFA ordered Zvezda to play next Tuesday's UEFA
Cup second-round first-leg tie against Olympique Lyon of France
in Bucharest because of the tensions over Yugoslavia's volatile
province of Kosovo. 
