death and Woosnam pulled his drive into the left-hand rough. He
could not reach the green in two and after conceding a par-four
to Woods, he missed from eight feet and the match was over.
</P>
<P>
Woosnam had led by three after only eight holes of the morning
session, but Woods won the 10th and 12th to be only one behind at
lunch.
</P>
