The match was all square when Woosnam ran up a double bogey
six at the 21st and Woods went in front for the first time when
he chipped in for an eagle at the next.
</P>
<P>
But it looked like his debut in the event would be short-lived
when Woosnam won three out of four holes from the 27th but he
could not close out the match.
